## 📚 Deployment Workflow

**When you modify the app:**

1. **Frontend changes (index.html):**
   - Edit in GitHub
   - Commit with descriptive message
   - Changes live immediately (GitHub Pages)

2. **Backend changes (Google Apps Script):**
   - Edit function in Apps Script
   - Save the file
   - Deploy → New Deployment (Web app)
   - Copy new deployment URL
   - Update `API_URL` in index.html (line 291-292) if URL changed
   - Commit to GitHub
   - Refresh app in browser

