## 💾 Database Schema

### Students (4 columns)
```
A: id (e.g., "s1")
B: name (e.g., "Marcus Bell")
C: active (TRUE/FALSE)
D: group (e.g., "Room 102")
```

### Sessions (6 columns)
```
A: id (e.g., "s1-20260709-001")
B: studentId (e.g., "s1")
C: rubricId (e.g., "JTT-304")
D: evaluatorName (e.g., "Luke Skywalker")
E: submittedAt (ISO datetime)
F: notes (session notes text)
```

### Scores (3 columns)
```
A: sessionId (links to Sessions)
B: skillId (e.g., "JTT304_Primary__s1")
C: score (0–5 or "NA")
```

